==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonjoinder
<hw>Non*join"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Law)</fld>
<def>The omission of some person who ought to have been made a plaintiff
or defendant in a suit, or of some cause of action which ought to be
joined.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nonjurant</ent>⟦br⟧
